      "text": [
        "859 - وَقَالَ اَلنَّبِيُّ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ: «كُلُّ وَاعِظٍ قِبْلَةٌ وَ كُلُّ مَوْعُوظٍ قِبْلَةٌ لِلْوَاعِظِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.859 - The Prophet, said:\n\"Every preacher is a Qiblah, and every one being preached to is a Qiblah for the preacher.\""
        ]
      }
    },
